    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Quae iacet hoc saxo maternis moribus <lb n="2"/>aequa cunctorumque dolor casta Boethio<lb break="no" n="3"/>la nobiliter nata clarissima femina Amand<lb break="no" n="4"/>i coniunx consimilis qui posuit titulum <lb n="5"/>o quam saeva dies bissenos i&amp;lt;n=M&amp;gt;<surplus>p</surplus>tulit ann<lb break="no" n="6"/>os qui<expan><ex>bu</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> vixit sancte coniuge cum proprio <lb n="7"/>Boethiola <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissima</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>emina</ex></expan> vixit anni<lb break="no" n="8"/>s <note>sic</note> XXV et menses VIIII dies III quae fuit <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">uxor</supplied> Amandi <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimi</ex></expan> annos XII et dies XVIIII 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1-6: elegische Disticha. Zwischen Z. 6 und 7 der Inschrift Darstellung eines Kreuzes mit Alpha und Omega und symmetrisch flankierenden Tauben.</p>
            </div>
